Class PropertyChangerConfigurer

  • java.lang.Object
    • VASSAL.configure.Configurer
      • VASSAL.build.module.properties.PropertyChangerConfigurer

  • public class PropertyChangerConfigurer
extends Configurer
    Configurer instance that allows a module editor to specify a PropertyChanger, i.e. the way in which a dynamic property will be updated by a player during a game
